org.seedstack.business.api.interfaces.finder

Class Result<Item>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.seedstack.business.api.interfaces.finder.Result<Item>
  • Type Parameters:
    Item - the representation type

    public final class Result<Item>
extends Object
    Symbolises a ranged result of representation retrieved from the persistence. It exposes:
    • The list: getResult(),
    • The list size: getResultSize(),
    • The full size of the whole request: getFullSizeRequest().
    Author:
    epo.jemba@ext.mpsa.com
